Class DICOMMammoPixelAnonymizer

  • public class DICOMMammoPixelAnonymizer
extends java.lang.Object
    The DICOMMammoPixelAnonymizer attempts to find PHI burned into a rectangle on either the left or right side of mammography images and blanks it out.
